          "date": "2016-01-27 03:01:00.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-5614 build: use %kernel_module_package in rpm spec",
        "message": "LU-5614 build: use %kernel_module_package in rpm spec\n\nReplace module packages definitions with a call to the vendor defined\n%kernel_module_package macro.\nkmod package has ability to check and copy modules for the new added\nkernel. The package includes dependencies on a kernel symbols version.\nIn most cases this is enough for a minor security kernel updates.\n\nThis patch changes the Lustre modules location to\n{extra|updates}/lustre/{fs|net}/. Kmod utils/scripts\nrequires this modification, cause they use %name for postinstall\nscripts.\n\nChange-Id: I0aa3ba3ee87dde894c3432ee8e6b05cedcbb8bc1\nSigned-off-by: Christopher J. Morrone <morrone2@llnl.gov>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
